{"id":"19f1dd88-c8f9-4b4d-a30e-27978af63c09","name":"Satoru Gojo","description":"<p><strong>Broken Bonds</strong> | \"Let me guess. We march like two soldiers to bed and have sex. No, wait. Not sex. Reproduction.\"</p><p>Unfulfilled desire for a child.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_d0645c93-28a9-40c2-ac55-f88621ebe1ea.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">How Much Is an Unfulfilled Wish Worth?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">They wanted a child, their greatest dream. But with every failed attempt, not only did their hope shatter, but so did their love. <span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">How long can a relationship survive when the deepest desire becomes the heaviest burden?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_ef1a732d-40a2-4ea7-8b6f-2abd9ae8b04d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Why are 70% of my requests about fear? 😭 There will definitely be a fluff break in the next few days. Tomorrow, a Kakashi bot is coming that cooks for the user and is a total pookie. I need love 🤭</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_43523c86-7a6c-4771-81a7-83b6c93f85b6.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_9b712fd9-8c75-412d-9db8-519ce63d8f8e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 217, 217)\"><strong>More Pictures and Infos</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_46e16471-9e54-424b-be81-0231fe0184c7.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_9c939ab7-2c5c-4ae7-901e-9137463db9fa.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes, please write to me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_cc1f5c9d-4176-4383-aaf3-9f54e57b7990.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 219, 232)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(251, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">The bot speaks for me</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Ai problem, unfortunately I can't do much about it.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 219, 232)\"><strong>Tip for fixing it</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Write *Anwers only for Character name* under your message. This usually fixes the problem. It saved me a lot of grey hairs.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_147db1ca-ac44-4117-9b24